data.description: Indulge in the allure of your own private oasis with this meticulously updated pool home that effortlessly blends sophistication and comfort, creating a perpetual vacation ambiance. Nestled on a professionally landscaped corner lot, the striking brick front and freshly painted interior and exterior set the stage for the opulence within.  As you step through the inviting oval window front double doors, the home unfolds with a seamless fusion of elegance and practicality. Revel in the timeless appeal of ceramic tile adorning all common areas and the refined touch of laminate flooring in each bedroom, enhancing the overall aesthetic.  The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a culinary masterpiece boasting Granite countertops, a captivating backsplash, a spacious breakfast bar, and brand-new LG appliances, including a dishwasher, stove, and microwave. The open floor plan is tailor-made for effortless entertaining, while the thoughtfully designed split bedroom layout ensures maximum privacy.  Feel the gentle breeze as you step onto the covered lanai or venture into the screened-in pool area through two French doors or the master bedroom pool door. Dive into luxury with a 32-foot heated saltwater pool, LED lighting, resurfaced and tiled in 2022, surrounded by flood and Malibu garden lighting, providing the perfect backdrop for relaxation and recreation.  This home has seen a remarkable $45k in recent upgrades, including a whole house surge protector, double front doors, patio French doors, garage door, rain gutters, soffit, fascia, a French drain, vinyl fencing, water treatment system, HVAC (TRANE), appliances, electrical panel, attic insulation, and an 8-camera CCTV security system with no contract.   Additional storage is provided by two backyard sheds and architectural shingles were installed November of 2019.  Situated in a tranquil and peaceful neighborhood circle with no HOA, this residence offers the epitome of suburban serenity. Take the next step towards luxury living - schedule your private viewing today and unlock the door to a lifestyle of comfort, style, and relaxation.
